<br>
Make sure you save $ for spells.<br>
<br>
As for armor I did most of the cleric quests with my paladin except for the BP which was given to me.  I went all ac but wisdom not hard to get either.  <br>
<br>
<ul><br>
<li>Gold Jasper Earrings (30 pp)<br>
<li>Savants Cap (30 pp)<br>
<li>Black Iron Medal (30 pp)<br>
<li>Silver Ruby Veil (150 pp)<br>
<li>SilverJasper Rings (5 pp)<br>
<li>Testament of Venear (quest)<br>
</ul><br>
<br>
After that most people go for AC I think, you could get some pieces of fine plate/bronze/banded.. Then just upgrade the Armor.<br>
