<br>
Halfling Cleric of Bristlebane. Decent starting stats, Wis/Agi/Stam/Str wise, racial hide and sneak. If invis is one of the areas where clerics have a weakness (something I hear from my cleric friends a good ammount), having racial hide should help some.<br>
<br>
Human Cleric of Innoruuk. Sure, you're blind. Given. But access to the Reagent Symbol of Innoruuk (the darkness one), Ivandyr's Hoop, and all of the Paineel quest gear (Helm, Mask, and Shield) as well as human racial smithing just seems. Well. Neat. <p><font size=1>
